These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Beverage: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
Hobby: board-games, gardening, hiking, sudoku
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is between Beverage:cola and Hobby:gardening##2
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Hobby:board-games##3
3. Beverage:hot-chocolate is somewhere between Beverage:tea and Beverage:cola##7
4. Hobby:gardening is in an even position##4
5. Beverage:tea is on the right of Hobby:hiking##1
6. Hobby:gardening is somewhere in a numerically lower position to Hobby:board-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Hobby      | hiking  | gardening | sudoku        | board-games |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
Pet: dog, goat, hedgehog, snake
Sport: cycling, rowing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. Sport:volleyball is somewhere between Sport:skateboarding and Pet:hedgehog##7
2. Pet:snake is somewhere in a numerically lower position to Pet:dog##5
3. Pet:snake is somewhere in a numerically higher position to Sport:volleyball##5
4. Pet:goat is on the left of Pet:snake##1
5. Sport:volleyball is between Sport:skateboarding and Sport:rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | goat       | snake         | dog     |
| Sport   | rowing   | volleyball | skateboarding | cycling |

