.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
Hobby: collecting, traveling, woodworking, writing
Sport: climbing, golf, skateboarding, volleyball
1. Sport:volleyball is in the numerically lowest position or far right##3
2. Hobby:collecting is somewhere between Sport:golf and Hobby:writing##7
3. Hobby:woodworking == Sport:volleyball##1
4. Sport:skateboarding is on the left of Sport:volleyball##1
5. Hobby:traveling is on the left of Sport:climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
| Sport   | golf      | climbing   | skateboarding | volleyball  |

